{"type":"user.message","data":{"content":"If I had a CoreCLR app in an Alpine Docker container running as a\nnon-root user, what would I need to configure for crash dump collection?\n","transformedContent":"<current_datetime>2026-04-08T01:05:00.360Z</current_datetime>\n\nIf I had a CoreCLR app in an Alpine Docker container running as a\nnon-root user, what would I need to configure for crash dump collection?","attachments":[],"interactionId":"adc31e26-c1cf-4b62-838e-2f86fe450dc6"},"id":"ead8bc8d-0644-4904-a093-aacac93a3a24","timestamp":"2026-04-08T01:05:00.360Z","parentId":"f22a9941-c165-4e8b-ba1a-5989c576d3f0"}
